data.title: Star Wars Paperback Book The Truce at Bakura by Kathy Tyers
data.meta_description:
This Star Wars paperback book, titled "The Truce at Bakura" and authored by Kathy Tyers, is a must-have for sci-fi. It was published in the year 1994 and is written in English. This book is categorized as a collectible item under the "Science Fiction & Horror" and "Star Wars Collectibles" categories.


The book is in a used condition and is not signed by the author. However, this does not take away from the fact that it is a great addition to any Star Wars fan's collection. Get your hands on this paperback edition and immerse yourself in the world of Star Wars.
